OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783720151
OL,3,CMosque effigy on Moygashel bonfire
OL,4,C'sickening and cowardly'
OL,6,FAn effigy of a mosque placed on top of
OL,7,Fa loyalist bonfire in Moygashel, Co
OL,8,FTyrone has been branded as an attempt
OL,9,Fto stir up hatred.
OL,11,FMuslim representatives have said it
OL,12,Fhas led to fears for the safety of
OL,13,Fmembers of their community in the run
OL,14,Fup to the lighting of bonfires across
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,17,FThe DUP has said effigies should not
OL,18,Fbe placed on bonfires but the party
OL,19,Fsaid it supported the right of freedom
OL,20,Fof expression.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
