PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783720151
OL,3,CMosque effigy on Moygashel bonfire
OL,4,C'sickening and cowardly'
OL,6,FPolice have said the display is being
OL,7,Ftreated as a hate-motivated criminal
OL,8,Foffence and officers continue to
OL,9,Fassess the situation.
OL,11,FA 56-year-old man has been arrested.
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,14,Fhas described the bonfire display a
OL,15,F"sickening and cowardly act of
OL,16,Fintimidation".
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@MO]
