PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783720151
OL,3,CMosque effigy on Moygashel bonfire
OL,4,C'sickening and cowardly'
OL,6,FThe Moygashel Bonfire Association has
OL,7,Fdescribed the bonfire as an act of
OL,8,F"political protest" against
OL,9,F"uncontrolled illegal mass
OL,10,Fimmigration".
OL,12,FSigns saying "Secure our borders" and
OL,13,F"End the threat of radical Islam" have
OL,14,Falso been placed on the pyre, which is
OL,15,Fmade up of pallets and is due to be
OL,16,Fset alight on Friday night.
OL,18,FAmnesty International described it as
OL,19,Fa "vile display" and a "blatant
OL,20,Fattempt to stir up anti-Muslim hatred
OL,21,Fand intimidate local families".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]qD@AOUrD@LO]tD@NOUtD@aO]uD@
OL,26,AAOUuD@aO]{D@COU{D@PO]{D@XOU}D@^O]
