PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1783720151
OL,3,CMosque effigy on Moygashel bonfire
OL,4,C'sickening and cowardly'
OL,6,FThe same bonfire site has attracted
OL,7,Fcontroversy in previous years.
OL,9,FLast year there was condemnation after
OL,10,Feffigies of migrants in a boat were
OL,11,Fburned on the Moygashel fire.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the PSNI said:
OL,14,F"Police are aware of the item placed
OL,15,Fon top of the bonfire in Moygashel.
OL,17,F"A 56-year-old man has been arrested
OL,18,Fon suspicion of contravention of
OL,19,FArticle 9 of the Public Order (NI)
OL,20,FOrder 1987.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
